Pre swafɛɛnlɛ mblɛ pre pe paara na Kristo mɛɛ chichie ŋga pe taa e na kre taanla kre.
Ŋgi na hin? Nyumu taan na nyumu susrom wa jaa chaa yili blo nunu nu.
Yire e leele mblɛ pe fraka kre yii, mu yo na ki fna pe ku ku, a pe n paara a e sɛ pe gbo gbo.
Nyiɛkpɔɔ kee kre pe nyunɔ mu tɛɛ kre yo mbo, “Ki fna e pe cheche, ŋgi na hin? Ni pe cheche.”
Kre na Nyiɛkpɔɔ na e yeeri, ŋgi na hin? Kristo wre titi na kala nya e tlo, mbe e u le mbe tuan, mbe taa u dumble na.
A fuŋgaami, ki leele mblɛ pe n Nyiɛkpɔɔ chin pre pe kawako na yire na pre n chaa na yire kefuɛn nyjɛ pini na, a ki tia pra e tɛɛlɛ.
<font color=teal>Peter Hlɛ Shiinwo</font>ShaaraaMi Simon Peter, Yesu Kristo sumifun, na u bituŋu wi mi. Mi pan hlɛ ŋga yiri na shie leele mblɛ pe yire o Nyiɛkpɔɔ, na o ŋmaashɔfun Yesu Kristo wre frakaa na, a pe shɔnlie kpɔɔ na wre lɛ pre pan.
Leele mblɛ pe taa pre titi nɛɛrɛ kee, na wejiniŋge sisaa kee na, mu Nyiɛkpɔɔ jaŋga le kewaa pre na u nyi.Kafinɛ kee nyinafɛɛnlɛ pre, pee gbun ni, a pe kee ka ma na ŋga kie pan ni. Pe n na fiɛ na pie yɛnyiŋgefɛɛnlɛ mblɛ pee wa nyjeeri wa pre tɛɛlɛ.
La, e na lee e dumiɛ, na o Tafun, na o ŋmaashɔfun Yesu Kristo wre chiɛn nu. Wre wo yi yɛnyiŋge fuŋgaami, mu sɛ su nyjila kro nu. Ami.
La, Kristo e ŋga Kpra Ŋumu wre, a ki tia e kro kpra kre chin.
Kena ni wolo mblɛ ni kori, na o jawala n o gbun pimi ni kee ka na kre, oo gbun ta mbe yire Nyiɛkpɔɔ yiɛ.
Yesu Kristo Dansiɛrɛ KeeYesu Kristo wi ndro ŋmba wra pan, a pra u ndra je na nyumu ni, a wra ku, a u nyimi na wo, nyumu chiin ma kra yili u nu, la, nyumu na nyimi chaara yira yili u nu mu wo. A Kpra Ŋumu wre titi ki dansiɛrɛ li, ŋgi na hin? Kpra Ŋumu wre pe kprafun.
Ni ŋmbrɔ ŋmba ni kori, ni nyiɛtali na kee kro ki nyu mbe mu ŋga, mbe mu pe gbaŋmba, imi na ni shɔ mu li na muu gbaŋmba kre.
Pra yo e pan na, “Na ble hɛnyi yire waa na dani kre, leele plɛ we yiri mbra e pini mbra tɛɛ, pre leele pre we taa pre titi niŋge sisaa kolo ŋga ki n pe Nyiɛkpɔɔ kolo na.”
Ni chin ni mɛɛ kre ndra na, e frɔ tɛɛ mu kala nya tataara, nde e n pra tun.
La, e chiɛri plɛɛ wa Sardis na, a pe n peyɛ tɔ na nɛɛrɛ ni. Ki tia mi na pre we nyaari dodonyi finyi nu, ŋgi na hin? Pe fna ma.
Kee Nyjɛ Yie Pan Kre HlɛA ndaa yurɔ hlɛ ka nya ŋmba wraa wa mu tni ŋujɔɔn kre na wre kalie, a pra nyunɔ ki lam, na ki krɔ na, mu ki nyu yii na yirɛ ni gbee nununu kɔɔnashin.
Yaka ma ki tia, Nyiɛkpɔɔ, na Mbɔɔpɔ wre krɔkun ble kre da, ŋmbi we jaa yire mbe ki shie hin?”
Kawako KeeBawa ndaa ndra yire na le, mna loo na nyuu wa tro nyjeeri haalee, mna na paara kpɔɔ mbo, “E atɛ, e atɛ. Leele mblɛ ee wa mu tni tra, e atɛ, ŋgi na hin? Na nyjeeri bitumblɔ taarɛ hamblɛ pre waa pe bnɔ yire fɔ kre, kanyana kpɔɔ we pan.”
A ndaa sɛ yo bituŋu wre pan na, u ni ŋga hlɛ fiɛn kre, a wra kna mna yo ni pan mbo, “Ki shɔ mu ka, kie tna mu nyuu na srɛ yi, la, na mu ki jɔli, kie sro krakra mu lɛɛ.”
A pra wre wɔɔ badaaŋga wre kun mu wa tra, wre wi wɔɔ lɔlɔ ŋmba pe yeeri Sutna wre, ŋmba u waŋgra kro fana kre. Pra wre na u bitumblɔ pre kro kun mu wa tra.
Pre leele pre lɛ mblɛ pe n chiɛlɛ chaara wru mu peyɛ tɔ na nɛɛrɛ ni kre. Ŋgi na, pe n le nɛɛrɛ kee nu. A mna Mbɔɔpɔ wre we sɛ kpan, pre leele mblɛ wa u kro. Pre Nyiɛkpɔɔ lɔ mu yili leweele kro nu, a pe pe u bijloe, mu Nyiɛkpɔɔ, na Mbɔɔpɔ wre ŋga.
Pre leele mblɛ pra mu sumifɛɛnlɛ,na mu kee nyanyofɛɛnlɛ nyimi kna mna wo kre,ki tia mu pe ŋga nyimi mbe pe gbɔ,ŋgi na hin? Pan pe fna.”
A nyjeeri bituŋu wre na kna mu yo ni pan mbo, “lɔɛ nyjɛ mna nya, a chlɔ tɛtiɛrɔɔ wre naa wa mu tni yi na kre, waŋgrɛ, na sele, na yolo kro leele lɛ.
Leele pre mana na ndru mu yili shiinwo na mbo,“Hallelujah!Chia kre shio,a ki wree wa mbra shie nyjeerinyjila kro nu.”
A ndaa mblɛ pe ku mu nyi kre nya, lekpɔɛ, na pe fiɛnfiɛn kro, a praa wa mu yire ŋujɔɔn kre yiɛ. A pra hlɛ nyaa nyaa mu tɛɛ. A pra hlɛ fɔŋgɔ ka nyaa, kre na pe ŋmaa hlɛ, a ŋmba wraa wa mu tni ŋujɔɔn kre na kre na mblɛ pe ku mu nyi kre kepelee tɔɔnri hlɛ yire nu, mna pe kpra kun.
La, yira ŋga ki n pe cheche ka wa le chia kre na, a lewo ŋmba u nyifɛɛrɛ kee pini, na kafinɛfɛɛnlɛ wa le ki na. Fɔ mblɛ mɛɛ pe nyunɔ Mbɔɔpɔ wre ŋmaa hlɛ kre nu pre chiin bɔkɔ.
